name: DELIVERY FLIGHT! WestJet's NEWEST 737 MAX 8 Snowy Arrival at Calgary Airport
description:
Welcome home, Tail 316! WestJet's 14th Boeing 737 MAX 8 was finally delivered to their Calgary base from Boeing Field on Friday evening, making it the carrier's first new delivery of a MAX since the grounding.

C-GWLK first flew in October of 2019, but had been stored with Boeing for well over a year, for obvious reasons. Great to see a new delivery after so long, and in some surprisingly nice snowy conditions. Plus, one more to add to the list of WestJet aircraft in the new livery!
